media:group.media:title: Can Elon Musk Save Iran? #shorts
media:group.media:description:
In case you missed it, mass protests are breaking out in Iran — this time after a 22-year-old woman was beaten to death for showing too much hair under her hijab. As Iran shuts down their internet and threatens journalists, Elon Musk’s Starlink offers a tyranny-proof solution.
